  "name": "Justaerin Terminator Squad",
  "titles": "Justaerin Terminator Squad",
  "lore": "One of the two elite formations within the wider Luna Wolves and later Sons of Horus Legion, the Justaerin were the pride of the First Company and of their Legion. Tasked with forming the ‘point of the spear’ of countless assaults, they fearlessly went where the fighting was thickest, their attacks usually directed at destroying the heart of an opposing target or conducting the decapitation strike of an enemy force. Early proponents of the use of Tactical Dreadnought Armour, these black-and-gold-clad killers relied on the resilience this granted to smash aside any resistance, butchering those who dared to stand before them.",
